Pulitzer Publishing Co said itincreased the retail price of the Sunday St. LouisPost-Dispatch to 1.00 dlrs a copy from 75 cts, effective June14.    The Post-Dispatch, which last increased the price of itsSunday paper in 1980, said it will receive 19 cts as its shareof the 25 cts increase.    For the quarter ended March 31, the Post had an averageSunday circulation of 556,620. Reuter&#3;